  "detailed_description": "The game allows you to be a motorcycle mechanic. This is not only about motorcycle repair, but also everything that is associated with running this business. Find deals in online auctions, repair motorcycles and sell at a profit. Sound budget management will allow you to grow. You can invest in more motorcycles to repair and develop your workshop. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/BG-intro.gif?t=1555408301\" ><br><br>You start your adventure in a small home workshop and grow it to become the best motorcycle workshops in the world. Test your bikes on a track, check the quality of your repairs and performance that can be improved by fine-tuning. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/SportsMotorcycle_Preview_GIF.gif?t=1555408301\" ><br><br>You can choose from 4 types of motorcycles: Chopper, Naked, Sport and Tourist. You get to choose which motorcycles you want to repair.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/biker-new-21-12.gif?t=1555408301\" >",
  "about_the_game": "The game allows you to be a motorcycle mechanic. This is not only about motorcycle repair, but also everything that is associated with running this business. Find deals in online auctions, repair motorcycles and sell at a profit. Sound budget management will allow you to grow. You can invest in more motorcycles to repair and develop your workshop. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/BG-intro.gif?t=1555408301\" ><br><br>You start your adventure in a small home workshop and grow it to become the best motorcycle workshops in the world. Test your bikes on a track, check the quality of your repairs and performance that can be improved by fine-tuning. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/SportsMotorcycle_Preview_GIF.gif?t=1555408301\" ><br><br>You can choose from 4 types of motorcycles: Chopper, Naked, Sport and Tourist. You get to choose which motorcycles you want to repair.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/989770/extras/biker-new-21-12.gif?t=1555408301\" >",
